    <item>
      <title>根据供应商风险规则，科技巨头将面临英国央行的更多审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/tech-giants-face-more-boe-scrutiny-under-supplier-risk-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[监管机构周二表示，与英国金融公司合作的大型科技公司将面临更严格的审查，因为他们制定了期待已久的新规则来应对关键第三方供应商带来的潜在风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/tech-giants-face-more-boe-scrutiny-under-supplier-risk-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 14:08:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
