    <item>
      <title>Netflix 称目前有 7000 万用户观看带有广告的节目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/netflix-says-70-million-users-now-watch-shows-with-advertising</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Netflix 公司表示，每月有 7000 万观众观看带有广告的节目，几乎是 5 月份总数的两倍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/netflix-says-70-million-users-now-watch-shows-with-advertising</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>AI 初创公司 Writer 在新一轮融资中估值 19 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/ai-startup-writer-valued-at-1-9-billion-in-new-funding-round</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Writer 是一家初创公司，旨在与 OpenAI 等公司竞争，向企业销售人工智能产品。该公司已完成新一轮融资，估值几乎增长了四倍，达到 19 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/ai-startup-writer-valued-at-1-9-billion-in-new-funding-round</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 14:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高通首席执行官认为，尽管需求上升，但 AI 芯片并不短缺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/qualcomm-ceo-sees-no-shortage-of-ai-chips-even-as-demand-rises</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高通公司首席执行官克里斯蒂亚诺·阿蒙表示，即使对支持人工智能的智能手机的需求不断上升，人工智能热潮也不会导致类似疫情期间的全球芯片短缺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/qualcomm-ceo-sees-no-shortage-of-ai-chips-even-as-demand-rises</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 13:36:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Shopify 因强劲的销售增长前景而飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/shopify-reports-third-quarter-revenue-that-beat-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Shopify Inc. 表示将在假日购物季保持快速销售增长，随后股价飙升，表明这家加拿大电子商务公司吸引大型企业的策略正在取得成效。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/shopify-reports-third-quarter-revenue-that-beat-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 12:12:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
